/*! \mainpage Belos to %Thyra Linear Solver Adapters

This doxygen collection documents a small amount of code that wraps
<tt>Belos::IterativeSolver</tt> objects to implement the
<tt>Thyra::LinearOpWithSolveBase</tt> and
<tt>Thyra::LinearOpWithSolveFactoryBase</tt> interfaces.  The subclass
<tt>Thyra::BelosLinearOpWithSolveFactory</tt> should be used by clients to
manage the creation of <tt>Thyra::LinearOpWithSolveBase</tt> objects.

<ul>

<li> \ref Belos_Thyra_adapters_grp : Documents the basic wrapper code
for used Belos to implement %Thyra linear solver objects.

<li> \ref Belos_Thyra_examples_grp : Gives some examples of the use of
the Belos to Thyra adapter code.

</ul>

*/

/** \defgroup Belos_Thyra_adapters_grp Belos to Thyra Linear Solver Adapter Code

\section Belos_Thyra_adapters_classes_sec Classes

<ul>

<li><tt>Thyra::BelosLinearOpWithSolveFactory</tt> : A general concrete
implementation of the <tt>Thyra::LinearOpWithSolveFactoryBase</tt> interface
that creates <tt>Thyra::BelosLinearOpWithSolve</tt> objects.

<li><tt>Thyra::BelosLinearOpWithSolve</tt> : A very general concrete
implementation of the <tt>Thyra::LinearOpWithSolveBase</tt> interface.
Clients should not create these objects directly but instead should use
<tt>Thyra::BelosLinearOpWithSolveFactory</tt> for that purpose.

</ul>

\section Belos_Thyra_examples_sec Examples

<ul>
<li> \ref Belos_Thyra_examples_grp
</ul>

*/

